author: Benedikt Schmitt
commit_message:
*fixed* issue #3 which has been introduced with the lock counter

The acquire() method can now be called inside a with statement without side effects:

  with lock.acquire():
    pass

*updated* docstrings

author: Benedikt Schmitt
commit_message:
The filelock classes are now always available and have been moved out of the *if msvrct: ... elif fcntl ... else* clauses.
The *FileLock* variable is now an alias for the best file lock available for the current platform. These changes are
completly backwards compatible.
